		updated whitelist unit tests

	* hoststats:
		removed ippaddr_cpp.h, now uses ip_to_str
		bugfixes
	
	* sip_bf_detector:
		improved signal handler

	* ignore build artefacts
	* minor bugfixes all over the Nemea-detectors

2017-06-08 Nemea-detectors-1.3.6
